Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:06.79,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&\pos(400,650)}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}的修理之後 我們回到了東京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置身於都市的喧囂之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使人不禁覺得在空守村度過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛已是很久遠的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的度假屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友辭去工作以後開始經營度假屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他邀請我有空的時候去他那裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你還沒領略過真正的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神明的職責」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型颱風17號依然維持著強勁的勢頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並將於今晚登陸房總半島
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我們還買了新的泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 你們不必拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人也只剩你們而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們居然會在這種天氣裡過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 因為有一個人強烈希望...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是抱著最後一絲希望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說垂死掙扎好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在暴雨中開車 感覺特別疲憊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來匡平也必須考取駕照才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濕濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漏雨?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面似乎雨勢很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.72,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(575,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 先讓{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}查看一下屋頂...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是 漏得真嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和室田先生說下 讓他給我們換個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒你先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說枸雅君的房間也漏雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這颱風真強勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我們的房間裡漏雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 被緊緊壓著動彈不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣下去的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 {\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒在洗澡 我去叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停電?偏偏這時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害 我明明被壓得動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃的力氣可真大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 幫我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要穿泳裝?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎還有很多事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也有男性在 這樣淋濕的時候就不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也穿 難得新買的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然泳裝本來不該是這時候穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不行 應該是徹底壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的倉庫裡似乎有發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太黑了什麼也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強勁的風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會倒下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r} 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那你替我拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然變得一片漆黑 什麼也看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像闖了大禍...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像撞上什麼東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 看樣子是沒受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 到底發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.12,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}被布條...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加快些 趁現在風勢減弱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 站直了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還算好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學 日日乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颱風過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天也放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個看上去要很費勁才能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救護車全部出車了 似乎要花點時間才能過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颱風這麼強勁 各處都會受到不小的影響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 從那邊下去之後就是海了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和日日乃同學一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意 室田先生只是腳受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你待在這裡也做不了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我們就接受他的好意去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風浪還很大 不可以游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 昨晚在倉庫裡的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  這次你不是表現得很活躍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 而且還救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(485,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}果然是善神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空守村?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好偏僻的鄉下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有國道經過就已經是奇蹟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主頁也只是裝裝樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是要去調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 申請沒被通過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的打算去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又不算什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得上次遭遇的人偶事件更適合空張先生去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問他們和人偶有某種關聯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 從圖書館裡借來的書都在這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那詩緒 這裡就暫時拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市裡的圖書館很大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 詩緒只見過村子裡的圖書館啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子裡的很小不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是非常小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去了圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幫我還借來的書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平 叔叔說城市的圖書館很大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 你還沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 忘記這裡還有一本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時換我來接班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人能行嗎 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 二個女孩才剛走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人也全部走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是頭大呢 要是客人全都想著這些事情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話乾脆弄個COSPLAY咖啡店之類的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 久違的家鄉怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡什麼都沒改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過日日乃同學似乎很喜歡那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是以客人的身份去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還算是個不錯的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已悟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開了村子25年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為已經完全與村子裡切斷了關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我還是太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生於那村莊的人是絕對離不開那村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是在說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說完之後我才初次意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:28.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六年前 我放棄當{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}的真正原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當自己失去理性的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白自己的體內也沉睡著與阿幾相同的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾 你現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了一本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MUSICA NOVA的最新刊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不先看看去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾先生..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 真是巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你坐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從匡平那聽說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的表情是這麼告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於老師的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和枸雅君的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有空守村那些事情的來龍去脈都差不多清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 你繼續說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還有件事情我想不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你對枸雅君的執著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你痛恨周遭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你一個人去解決不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有足夠的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要把枸雅君給牽連進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡匡平嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不管怎樣這都和你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是否出於本人的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人與人之間就是會扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你和瀨能老師一樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真敢說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂了 回到剛才的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於匡平的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和神社的那群蠢人都沒有發現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的體內沉睡著黑暗且巨大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君有那種力量?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一直是個大少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計還沒發現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:17:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 說不定就是發現了所以才一直躲著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛想到 如果把你怎麼樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也會拿出真本事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 在這裡打鬥的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進步了不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾 老實點回村子裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:04.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}不是為了讓你破壞和殺戮而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是為了什麼而存在的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救人之類的 總之是為了做善事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做善事?救人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:40.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&\pos(640,650)}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不巧 我們的神只會破壞和殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這是為什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為裡面裝的是人心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視裡放過的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對面 在對面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我轉告匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的遊戲還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們碰到阿幾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學 那傢伙說了什麼過分的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說他對你亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在 不會讓他做那種事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學 請你開門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得非常火大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有與這件事有關的人都不按常理 我行我素
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曖昧而意有所指地讓人陷入混亂之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來還用高高在上的眼光去嘲笑別人的無知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學 日日乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉能讓我一個人靜靜...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癡漢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工口 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花心大蘿蔔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:49.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾說{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}只會破壞與殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說那是人心所為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管打算去做什麼樣的善事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:05.28,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}還是只會淪為會破壞和殺戮的道具嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然像他說的裡面如果裝的是人心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的還是你自身不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是這麼期望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.14,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}便會成為善神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:31.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想變成那樣的神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 哪還有什麼別的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 桐生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡空氣還是一樣混濁呢

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也同樣為你送上神樣DOLLS講座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.19,0:23:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天居然是我的特別專場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖吼理也十分地高興
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.34,0:23:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有各種各樣的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的表情就不必介紹給大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,staff staff
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 因緣的漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的話就詛咒你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

